messages.content: I need to schedule a task: Launch Minecraft in 10 seconds
OK. I have scheduled Minecraft to launch in 10 seconds.
What is using up most of my storage?

Your disk has had 83 GB read and 110 GB written. I cannot tell you which specific files or folders are using the most storage. I can tell you that the top processes by CPU usage are: System Idle Process, MsMpEng.exe (Windows Defender), System, dwm.exe (Desktop Window Manager), Code.exe (VS Code), qcdpps.exe, Copilot.exe, MuseHub.exe and PAD.Console.Host.exe (Power Automate). MsMpEng.exe is using a significant amount of memory.
what is the main CPU killer in my computer?

The top processes by CPU usage are: System Idle Process, MsMpEng.exe (Windows Defender), System, dwm.exe (Desktop Window Manager), Code.exe (VS Code), qcdpps.exe, Copilot.exe, MuseHub.exe and PAD.Console.Host.exe (Power Automate). It may be that Windows Defender or VS Code are the main CPU killers.
